update.changes:
JEM 2.3.6 released on May 2 2023. Last JEM version for Jomola 3 with PHP8 compatibility. Please refer to the change log for details.;
If you use template overrides please note that all views have been changed and there is a good chance that your overrides won't work as expected. So please check the changes and adapt your files.;
Versions previous to 2.3.2 will not install correctly on Joomla 3.10.1!;
This version of JEM is necessary for migration to JEM 4 in Joomla!4. You will have to wait for JEM 4.x for that!

JEM 4.0.0 released on July 3 2023. First JEM version offering Joomla 4 and PHP8 compatibility. Please refer to the change log for details.;
If you use template overrides please note that all views have been changed and there is a good chance that your overrides won't work as expected. So please check the changes and adapt your files.;
For migration from JEM on Joomla 3.10.11, don't uninstall, only disable plugin and modules. Versions previous to 2.3.5 will not migrate correctly.;
This version of JEM is full compatible with Joomla!4.
